| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2560 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 96b0cb89-2f2d-5589-a5ca-5ee455398a3d"
